e":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:15:28.000Z","msg":"如果係要係機場黎多次64先安樂<br />\n我諗我無資格叫人散定留<br />\n不過一陣機場見<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"701d0fbea4954eb33e8047b1084f636f04a9f819","tid":1460491,"uid":126043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3e5fb990cb24c65e2609ff471e171dece73098b","tid":1460491,"uid":49753,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"afba8628ad9c0f73aed949580d57f4d23c64abed","tid":1460491,"uid":126043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:38:45.000Z","msg":"我想問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實本身機場就已經有機場特警 <br />\n而且並非用布袋彈 橡膠子彈 <br />\n而係實彈<br />\n<br />\n警察今日直情唔敢承認葵芳地鐵站係室內<br />\n代表其實警察冇可能喺機場內使用催淚彈<br />\n<br />\n咁係咪即係 警察如果係機場內使用武力<br />\n就必然係最高嘅武力<br />\n<br />\n^咁即係假設佢哋會對機場進行完全性嘅清場？<br />\nJust like 64?<br />\n<br />\n否則, 機場會係一直安全和平?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:40:38.000Z","msg":"我剩係一句，有冇危險？yes or no?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:18:26.000Z","msg":"你哋啲咩問題? <br />\n<br />\n香港依家邊度唔危險㗎？ <br />\n仲洗抗爭嘅？<br />\n返去做順民啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9866b3940fcb9d2c317c453833549cb793b4271","tid":1460491,"uid":126043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36f319e1e84f75a94874a7077febe3019d43964d","tid":1460491,"uid":90692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3e5fb990cb24c65e2609ff471e171dece73098b","tid":1460491,"uid":49753,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"afba8628ad9c0f73aed949580d57f4d23c64abed","tid":1460491,"uid":126043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:38:45.000Z","msg":"我想問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chick